metadata.description:
Art minted as a celebration for 2 years of my first art minted on the blockchain, 26/09/2020.  
6 editions to my 1/1 collectors: ddaavvee, Camoleite, Kolmetuhatta, Inspector9, Melroseparkllc, dduarte. 2 editions to my very first collectors & supporters: Chafomon and JustinJ.  
Extra editions are available for the public.

Made in June 2022.
